title: Valar Rereadis: A Game of Thrones Review
description:
We are joined by Lady Gwyn of Radio Westeros to review themes, arcs, surprises and best moments from Book 1. We did chapter by chapter, now it's time to do the book as a whole! Published September 23, 2019.
